          smallrule
"><div class="wsj-article-page-rule"></div></div><h3> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/what-i-learned-about-vacationing-from-my-workaholic-sonand-his-phone-44ae2d5c?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">What I Learned About Vacationing From My Workaholic Son—and His Phone</a></h3><h4> When a millennial son arrives at his parents&#39; Wi-Fi-challenged cottage in Brittany, the search for a signal forges unexpected connections of a different, cross-generational sort. <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/what-i-learned-about-vacationing-from-my-workaholic-sonand-his-phone-44ae2d5c?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">Read the story.</a> </h4><div class="media-object scope-
